<template>
{{ response }}
</template>

<script>
import axios from 'axios'

export default {
    data(){
    return {
        response: "",
    }
},
name: 'ShowDataBase',
method:{
    async getArticles() {
        const endpoint = "/api/v1/image/";
        this.response = await axios.get(endpoint);
    },
}
}
</script>
